title: Sippy Cup Coffee & How to Build a Life
description:
Tasia and Camo are back this week answering fan questions! From talking about their first impressions of each other, to giving advice to twenty-somethings who are feeling lost, this episode is chalked full of funny stories and inspiring advice. Tune in to learn what Tasia and Camo think about Prenups, the finale of Euphoria, and so much more!!
For 50% off your 1st Care/of order, go to TakeCareOf.com and enter code “unfazed50”!
